creator: Emily Dickinson
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 17 recordings of There's a certain slant of light by Emily Dickinson. This was the Weekly Poetry Project for December 15, 2013. Read in English by David Lawrence; elisecandel; raggsy; Garth Burton; Isana; Joe Brenneman; Jason Mills; Jannie Meisberger; John Sercel; Kanta; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Maria Kasper; nbvoices; Patrick Wallace; ravenotation; and Winston Tharp. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (7MB)
